token_info.description: Created by @MathMakesArt on 2021/03/25. Generative geometric pattern animation using the phrase "#OBJKT4OBJKT" as input, written in p5.js and minted as HTML. This is my entry to the @DiverseNftArt x HicEtNunc OBJKT4OBJKT swap event. The string-to-pixelart encoding scheme used here was first displayed in my "25 Hashes" piece (https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/9953) and on Twitter (https://twitter.com/mathMakesArt/status/1370339297279279107).
